title: Cross-version Extension `R5.ConceptMap.group` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `ConceptMap.group` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `ConceptMap.group` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

`ConceptMap.group` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `ConceptMap.group` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4B: `ConceptMap.group` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4: `ConceptMap.group` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Element `ConceptMap.group` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `ConceptMap.group`, but has no comparisons.
